"amatogadhā amatapariyosānā’ti, iti kho panetaṃ vuttaṃ kiñcetaṃ paṭicca "
"vuttaṃ?"
msgstr ""
"‘When the perception of death is developed and cultivated it’s very fruitful "
"and beneficial. It culminates in the deathless and ends with the deathless.’ "
"That’s what I said, but why did I say it?"

msgctxt "an7.49:4.2"
msgid ""
